"tid":83071,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"練"},{"pid":"aa219c59a484c6b9baab84e20ce9b4e684b2512a","tid":83071,"uid":50892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"每日都要練，出盡力bar，啱啱開係會痛/難都閪咁，想成功就一定要比心機/時間去練<br />\nPS 過來人，好撚鐘意彈結他"},{"pid":"6f08fe334b33be846cdf2450382e338801652435","tid":83071,"uid":38183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練</blockquote><br />\n練"},{"pid":"181d869fa6405612b7f4f88aec2195f9693e3736","tid":83071,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"慢慢練到你隻手嘅肌肉足夠你用到啱嘅力為至<br />\n唔好亂用力<br />\n開頭太大力練，傷咗手就得不償失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾啲時間等手指手掌前臂肌肉去develop啦"},{"pid":"06468949a8445f37a07787335d31772fec07c815","tid":83071,"uid":45461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"用手指側會實d"},{"pid":"e4e416fdb0aba68fa8a186a0c043352466e255e2","tid":83071,"uid":77831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"彈多啲就得架喇 (廢話，但係事實)<br />\n認真，你試下側少少隻手指，我因為正放時，關節位會掂唔到啲線，打側用力按落去會好啲<br />\n但bar 5條線就冇問題，6條個陣，可能因為手指短，啲聲都一時時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3634605fa37169f9c1f13cd992d2812020382a2f","tid":83071,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"出盡力都禁唔實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24439cca0e3972ebde70ea7c92c89bce34c04178","tid":83071,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改名自答係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f9e6e3d7f32824f67b8876d6671ec3d2d58a4e","tid":83071,"uid":19299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"枝結他靚貨定垃圾<br />\n<br />\n盡量用食指右側bar"},{"pid":"4dbd9fc5503b510942a2ea8769cc74aa6b0d5b4d","tid":83071,"uid":29131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"Bar chord既2，3，4手指都係平時咁禁 基本上唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係食指要練 逐條逐條弦咁禁 先處理第6同第1條弦 禁到出聲就唔好放 再試下第2條 加埋個3隻手指基本上彈晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8fd30d228980d8963f275f25dca4e9a5552b9d","tid":83071,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"用木結他練力"}]}